Using XLOOKUP, I retrieved the values for the customer names, email and country columns in the orders sheet from the Customer sheet
For columns coffe type, roast type, size and unit price, Using Match function, I retrieved the row and column numbers
Using the Index function I retrieved the values for the coffee type, roast type, size and unit price columns
I calculated the sales columns by multiplying quantity against the unit price . I used formatting option to display the sales in USD
I used logical IF function to display the coffee type name and roast name
